        Accessibility
    </h2>
    <p>All stops feature an ADA ramp from wide and accessible sidewalks for people using wheelchairs, strollers, etc.
        Also, platform edges are equipped with tactile strips for people with vision impairments.
        Level boarding ensures there are no ramps or steps to worry about between platform and vehicle at all stops.
    </p>

