        Maps and information
    </h2>
    <p>All stops display a route map and essential passenger information.
        Note that real-time arrivals are only available on the <a href="https://itsmarta.com/marta-on-the-go.aspx">MARTA app</a>.
        Detailed schedules are available on the <a href="https://itsmarta.com/Atlanta-Street-Car-Info.aspx">Atlanta Streetcar page</a> and on the MARTA app.</p>

